        <p class="el-el-1782630570306-h3bi0zk9c">E-Commerce Platform</p>
        <p class="el-el-1782630570307-th3mwhfsw">Web Design • 2023</p>
        <p class="el-el-1782630570307-80w3nkgr5">A modern e-commerce solution with seamless checkout experience.</p>
        <section class="el-el-1782630570307-hp51w6477"></section>
        <p class="el-el-1782630570307-88wx7w5uu">Brand Identity System</p>
        <p class="el-el-1782630570307-mxnqitnp7">Branding • 2023</p>
        <p class="el-el-1782630570307-gsvw5ys44">Complete visual identity for a tech startup including logo and guidelines.</p>
        <section class="el-el-1782630570307-z7nmw1bcx"></section>
        <p class="el-el-1782630570307-0w79d91me">Mobile Banking App</p>
